\pard\plain \tx1123\tx1685\tx2246\tx2794\tx3355\tx3917\tx4478\tx5040\tx5602\tx6163\tx6725\fi720\ri-720\sl288\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Tell me Mandri, is that why we found you dead in the Junei hills? Were you looking for burgeons? What\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 you were high and forgot to bring water?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Another question,\u8221\'94 said Moto. \u8220\'93Answer me honestly\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 are you stupid? Be honest, there\u8217\'92s no shame in it\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 are you unusually dumb?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mandri laughed at the bluntness, but his laugh tapered off because Moto was dead serious. The man really thought he was stupid.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m not dumb. I\u8217\'92m telling you what I know.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Moto looked up at the sky as if to prepare himself for an unavailing labor. Then he said, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93The way I see it, either you\u8217\'92re being short with me because you think you can get away with it, which means you\u8217\'92re stupid, or you're doing it because you don\u8217\'92t understand the meaning of the word \u8216\'91thorough\u8217\'92, which would also mean you\u8217\'92re stupid. So which is it?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mandri shrugged.}
